# zvava.org
static website generator (html and gemini) for my personal website

## development
run `node make` to create out/, out/gemini/, and out/www/, then generate contents

run `webserver 80 out/www/` (`npm i -g webserver`) to debug html output

run `agate --content out/gemini/ --host localhost` to debug gemini output

## production
make sure all changes are committed and pushed

run `node publish` and enter password to sync changes with the webserver

`out/gemini/` contents will be copied to `/var/gemini/content/`

`out/www/` contents will be copied to `/var/www/`
